\newlabel{fig:framework}{{2}{2}{Overview of the EduIllustrate system. Given a K-12 STEM problem, the EduIllustrate Agent generates a structured explanation document through a four-stage pipeline. The resulting output is evaluated using an 8-dimension rubric validated against human expert raters via both automated LLM-as-judge and human evaluation protocols}{figure.caption.1}{}}
